<item>
            <title>[CASSANDRA-6380] SSTableReader.loadSummary may leave an open file</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-6380</link>
                <project id="12310865" key="CASSANDRA">Apache Cassandra</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;When &lt;tt&gt;SSTableReader.loadSummary&lt;/tt&gt; catches &lt;em&gt;IOException&lt;/em&gt; it tries to delete &lt;tt&gt;summariesFile&lt;/tt&gt;, but the &lt;tt&gt;iStream&lt;/tt&gt; is still open and the file is locked, so &lt;tt&gt;FileUtils.deleteWithConfirm&lt;/tt&gt; fails, at least on Windows&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12680110">CASSANDRA-6380</key>
            <summary>SSTableReader.loadSummary may leave an open file</summary>
